column2:
Just an interesting observation about reviews -
there's 3 types of ppl who make negative reviews about half-life 2:
1)Trolls - "cant sex the breen/alyx" / "l won't pick up the can";
2)People that are not happy that there's still no Half-life 3;
3)People that expect too much from the game after numerous eulogies about the game.
